  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet nu eſſam mehſ wiſſi\nka weens Neſchkibſtajs/ un wiſſa\nmuhsu Taifniba ka fabrnairra\nDrehbe. Un mehſ wiſſi nowih-\nſtam ka Lappa/ un muhsu Greb-\nki aiſwedd muhs ka tas Wehjſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un neweens irr kas tawn\nWahrdu peefanz/ kas uſimoh-\nſtohs un pee tewis tivertohe. Jo\ntu apſlep tawu Waigu no mumis/\nun leez muhs niḣzin iſnihkt zaur\nmuhsceem Grehkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad/ KUNGS/ tu\neſſi muhsu Tehws/ mehſ eſſam\nMahls/ un tu eſſi muhsu Pohd-\nneeks/ un mehſ wiſſi eſſam taws\nRohku Darbe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne apſkaistees KUNGS\ntik tohti/ un ne peeminn to No-\nſegumu muhschtgi/ rangi/ us-\ntuhko jelle ſcho/ ka mehſ wiſſa ta-\nwi Landis eſſam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawi ſwehti Piſſahti\nirr par Tukſneſi tapnuſchi/ Ziana\nirr Tuſniba/ Jeruſaleme irr poh-\nſta Weeta tapnuſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Muhsu twehts un goh-\ndigś Nams/ eeſſh ka muhsu\nTehwi tewi flaweja/ irr ar Ug-\nguni ſadedſinahts/ un wiſſas\nmuhsu ſkaistas Leetas irr bohjá\ngahjuſchas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "KUNGS/ woj tit pahr\nſchiim Leetahn apturrefees? woj\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tomehr ir no teem wehl few we\nDsimimu poſurreht: 8 Draude teem\nkahpajeemi ar Sohhinu: 11. Bet teem\nzigeem apſohla wiſſh Preeku un Sweh-\nmu: 13/ 16. Un ka wiſſh jaunu Debl\nun Semmi raddihs: 17.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "S tohpu meklehts\nTeem/ kas (pehz ma-\nnis) ne waizaja/\ntohpu atrasts no teem/ kas ma-\nni ne mekleja. Es eſmu fazz-\nus teem Laudim/ kas man-\nWahrdu ne peefanze: Reds/ fe-\ncē eſmu/ Reds/ ſche es eſmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es iſpleſchu ſawas Ro-\nkas zaurn Deenu us pahrgatu-\ngeem Laudim/ kas us weenu\nlabbu Jeſtu staiga/ pehz ſawa-\npachahn Dohmaſchanahn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee irr Laudis/ kas ween-\nmebr mann apkaitina/ kas ma-\nnā Preeſchā uppure Dahrsō\nun us Steegetcem kwehpina\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas pee Rappenehm fehsc\nun zaur Nahti (Deewe-\nBedreś paleek/ un ehd Zuh-\nGakku/ un negantas Sullas\nwinnu Traukds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas ſakka: Turrajs pa-\npee ſewim/ ne nahz tuwu\nman/ jo es eſmu ſwehtaks ne-\ntu. Schee buhs par Duhmee-\neeſſh mannas Duſmibas/wee-\nUgguns/ kas zauru Deenn deg\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangi/ tas irr man-\nPreeſchā rakſihts/ es ne zee\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
